title: UNBROKEN - Best Motivational Speech Compilation
itunes:title: UNBROKEN - Best Motivational Speech Compilation
itunes:subtitle: Motiversity
description:
UNBROKEN! Courage isn't having the strength to go on, it is going on when you don't have the strength. We will all die one day, but at least we will die UNBROKEN.


Best Motivational Speeches Compilation featuring a new speech from Bobby Maximus (https://bit.ly/BobbyMaximusMotiversity), Elliot Hulse (https://bit.ly/ElliottHulseMotiversity) and Logan Taylor (https://bit.ly/LoganTaylorMotiversity).


Music by Really Slow Motion (https://bit.ly/RSMMusic), Paul Elhart (http://bit.ly/2SiEaIN), EMM (https://bit.ly/EpicMotiversityMusic) and Borrtex (https://www.youtube.com/Borrtex).


Hosted on Acast. See acast.com/privacy for more information.
